\" 提示\n\n### 4. 视觉风格\n\n- 简约风格，深色背景 + 亮色蛇身\n- 蛇身：绿色系，蛇头略深\n- 食物：红色圆形\n- 网格：浅色细线（可选，不突兀）\n- 分数显示在画布上方或右上角\n\n### 5. 分数系统\n\n- 每个食物 10 分\n- 实时显示当前分数\n- 使用 localStorage 保存历史最高分\n- 游戏结束时显示当前得分和历史最高分对比\n\n### 6. 难度\n\n- 固定速度（经典模式），蛇移动速度适中（约 150ms 每步）\n- 不需要难度选择\n\n## 技术决策\n\n- **技术栈**：纯 HTML5 + CSS3 + JavaScript（ES6+）\n- **渲染方式**：HTML5 Canvas API\n- **部署方式**：单文件 `index.html`，浏览器直接打开\n- **零依赖**：不使用任何第三方库或框架\n- **兼容性**：现代浏览器（Chrome/Firefox/Edge/Safari 最新版）\n\n## 不包含的功能\n\n- 无音效\n- 无排行榜（仅本地最高分）\n- 无特殊食物（加速/减速/加分）\n- 无多关卡\n- 无移动端适配\n- 无多语言\n- 无多人模式\n\n## 验收标准\n\n1. 浏览器打开 index.html 即可开始游戏\n2. 蛇可以通过方向键/WASD 平滑控制方向\n3. 吃到食物后蛇身正确增长，分数正确累加\n4. 撞墙或撞自己后游戏正确结束\n5. 游戏结束后可重新开始\n6. 历史最高分通过 localStorage 持久化\n7. 暂停/继续功能正常\n8. 画面流畅，无明显卡顿\n"},"output":"{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"path\": \".specforge/specs/WI-018/intake.md\",\n  \"size\": 2721\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1780101601211,"end":1780101601235}},"id":"prt_e7652d7ad001w52Wg75w6ApKfI","sessionID":"ses_189b03ce3ffezni9hA2ZeUXgHs","messageID":"msg_e76529d78001rriRbu20L0a1t7"},{"reason":"tool-calls","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":25056,"input":683,"output":821,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":23552}},"cost":0,"id":"prt_e7652d7d8001vDjQw2a43AuVJu","sessionID":"ses_189b03ce3ffezni9hA2ZeUXgHs","messageID":"msg_e76529d78001rriRbu20L0a1t7"}]},{"info":{"parentID":"msg_e765232c2001thYp9Y709Tvhxx","role":"assistant","mode":"sf-orchestrator","agent":"sf-orchestrator","path":{"cwd":"D:\\code\\temp\\wzq","root":"/"},"cost":0,"tokens":{"total":25161,"input":903,"output":66,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":24192}},"modelID":"glm-5.1","providerID":"zhipu-coding-plan","time":{"created":1780101601257,"completed":1780101604993},"finish":"tool-calls","id":"msg_e7652d7e90010AevMfRY7KK9o5","sessionID":"ses_189b03ce3ffezni9hA2ZeUXgHs"},"parts":[{"type":"step-start","id":"prt_e7652e389001R132kjxIpw2VW3","sessionID":"ses_189b03ce3ffezni9hA2ZeUXgHs","messageID":"msg_e7652d7e90010AevMfRY7KK9o5"},{"typ